DistanceFromListener: Uunits between Listener and Sound Source.
SpeedRelativeToListener: Uunits per second change in distance between Listener and Sound Source.
SpeedOfSourceEmitter: Uunits per second change in world location of Sound Source.
SpeedOfListener: Uunits per second change in world location of Listener.
SpeedOfAngleDelta: Degrees per second change in Angle of Source from Listener.
